env PAGER=cat man timing_check_timing_signal_level_low_to_high_thr eshold
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_check_t...high_threshold(25.10)  timing_check_t...high_threshold(25.10)

Name
       timing_check_timing_signal_level_low_to_high_threshold

Syntax
       timing_check_timing_signal_level_low_to_high_threshold double

       Default: 0

       Sets  the  threshold  value for warning the signal level difference be-
       tween driver and receiver voltages, when the driver is at a lower volt-
       age than the receiver voltage.

       The  software  shows  the  signal  level  warnings  (check_timing  sig-
       nal_level)  that report the net driver/receiver pin pairs for which the
       pin voltage does not match. The signal level warning  messages  can  be
       filtered based on these threshold values.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

